OL,4,CCovid: Home-working officials won't get
OL,5,Cpaid less, says minister
OL,6, Business Secretary Kwasi Kwarteng has
OL,7, rejected the idea that civil servants
OL,8, should be paid less if they continue
OL,9, working from home.
OL,11,FIt comes after an unnamed cabinet
OL,12,Fminister told the Daily Mail it was
OL,13,Funfair for those returning to the
OL,14,Foffice not to be paid more.
OL,16,FBut Mr Kwarteng said this would set
OL,17,Fcolleagues against each other.
OL,19,FAnd he added that flexible working -
OL,20,Fwith people working from home some of
OL,21,Fthe time - was "here to stay".
